OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780492266
OL,3,CFundraiser set up for rider Maria
OL,4,CCostello 'currently paralysed' after
OL,5,CTT crash
OL,7,FA fundraiser has been set up to
OL,8,Fsupport Isle of Man TT rider Maria
OL,9,FCostello MBE, following a sidecar
OL,10,Fcrash during qualifying that has left
OL,11,Fher paralysed.
OL,13,FDriver Costello and passenger Shaun
OL,14,FParker came off the course, after
OL,15,Fhitting a hare near Brandish corner
OL,16,Ftowards the end of a lap of the
OL,17,FMountain Course.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780492266
OL,3,CFundraiser set up for rider Maria
OL,4,CCostello 'currently paralysed' after
OL,5,CTT crash
OL,7,FBoth were taken to Noble's Hospital
OL,8,Fwith extensive injuries, before being
OL,9,Fairlifted to Aintree Hospital in
OL,10,FLiverpool for further treatment.
OL,12,FCostello is described as 'stable', but
OL,13,Fwill need surgery to 'regain use of
OL,14,Fher legs'.
OL,16,FA GoFundMe page has been set up to
OL,17,Fhelp with her care, with thousands of
OL,18,Fpounds raised in the first few hours.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780492266
OL,3,CFundraiser set up for rider Maria
OL,4,CCostello 'currently paralysed' after
OL,5,CTT crash
OL,7,FPassenger Shaun Parker posted a video
OL,8,Fon social media from his hospital bed,
OL,9,Fsaying he was receiving treatment for
OL,10,Fa broken foot, ribs, clavicle, jaw,
OL,11,Fankle and knee. He also suffered a
OL,12,Fcollapsed lung and blurred vision.
OL,14,FPosting on the page, a spokesperson
OL,15,Ffor Maria said: 'Maria will need
OL,16,Fspecialist help with physio care and
OL,17,Fperhaps surgeries to hopefully help
OL,18,FMaria regain use of her legs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
