OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780492266
OL,3,CFundraiser set up for rider Maria
OL,4,CCostello 'currently paralysed' after
OL,5,CTT crash
OL,7,F'One thing that is clear from Maria's
OL,8,Finjuries is that this will have a
OL,9,Flifelong impact on her, not just
OL,10,Fpreventing and affecting a return to
OL,11,Fsport but impacting Maria's every day
OL,12,Flife.
OL,14,F'Maria will need to adapt almost all
OL,15,Faspects of her life.
OL,17,F'After a life of giving everything to
OL,18,Fa sport she loves, she will now turn
OL,19,Fthat determination to recovery and
OL,20,Frecuperation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780492266
OL,3,CFundraiser set up for rider Maria
OL,4,CCostello 'currently paralysed' after
OL,5,CTT crash
OL,7,F'From the initial determination of her
OL,8,Finjuries it is already clear that
OL,9,FMaria will need to move house or make
OL,10,Fhouse alterations, with accessibility
OL,11,Fadjustments needed wherever she is
OL,12,Fbased.
OL,14,F'She will need an adapted bed, shower,
OL,15,Fkitchen, stairlift and specialist
OL,16,Fvehicle for transport.
OL,18,F'Maria will need further surgery over
OL,19,Fthe coming weeks and months and
OL,20,Frequire specialist rehab and physio
OL,21,Fsupport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780492266
OL,3,CFundraiser set up for rider Maria
OL,4,CCostello 'currently paralysed' after
OL,5,CTT crash
OL,7,F'Maria is beyond determined to bounce
OL,8,Fback and apply every ounce of focus to
OL,9,Fbeing back as well as possible.
OL,11,F'Maria's recovery is highly expensive
OL,12,Fand after a career spent raising money
OL,13,Ffrom sponsors and backers for racing
OL,14,Fwe now find ourselves asking for
OL,15,Fsupport for a very different but all
OL,16,Ftoo real problem.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780492266
OL,3,CFundraiser set up for rider Maria
OL,4,CCostello 'currently paralysed' after
OL,5,CTT crash
OL,7,F'Whatever you can give will go some
OL,8,Fway to helping Maria's recovery. We
OL,9,Fhugely appreciate any support and
OL,10,Fpromise to continue to update you all
OL,11,Fon progress.'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
